E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Oh! I'm getting blamed for this now? Oh of course.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~噢！现在都怪我了是吧？那确实。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Shut up, Lou! He didn't mean anything by it.
~z~Don't underestimate it, Luis. The snatch has brought down empires bigger than our own.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~别低估女人，Luis。娘们搞垮过比我们更大的帝国。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Oh, funny shit. One of the benefits of running a club is a thorough ID check on any potential interaction.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~哦，别开玩笑了。夜店经理的好处之一，就是对客人的身份知根知底。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yeah you'll be holding back more than that, you fucking prick. Any debt Tony had died with him. Get the fuck out of here.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~是的，你要忍住的可多多了，他妈的混蛋。Tony欠的钱都一笔勾销了。赶紧消失吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Never trust a Mex to do a man's job. That's what my mamma taught me.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~永远不要把男人的工作交给老墨。这是妈妈教我的。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Don't you mean it's one of the joys of borrowing money you can't pay back?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~我看应该是不自量力借一大笔钱吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yeah, well, if you weren't out chasing tail, and this was a two man operation like it should be,
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~是啊，要不是你在外面瞎转悠，我们的合作经营肯定好好的。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Again with the sarcasm. It's really beneath you.
~z~Anything happens to Rock, we'll be blamed. We gotta go, Lou.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~Rock有什么闪失，我们都得背锅。快走啊，Lou。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yeah, I can. I got better things to be doing than babysitting the snot nosed prick.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~能啊，怎么不能。比起照顾这个鼻涕虫，我还有更好的事情能做。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~So, we lost Rocco, but I'm thinking he'll come find us soon enough.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~虽然跟丢了Rocco，但他很快就会来找我们吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~The emphasis is on business, bro. You can keep your crabs to yourself.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~重点在于生意，兄弟。螃蟹你自己留着吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~There they are. The spic and the fag.
~z~Shit, Tone. I wish you'd told me you got yourself in these kind of scrapes when you asked me to work for you.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~妈的，Tone。让我当你手下的时候你咋不说会遇到这种麻烦。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You hit him with some balls when I tell you to. You think you can that do for me, Louise?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~等我发话了，你就给他来几球。有没有信心，Louise？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Oh I don't know. Just get us out of here and shut up.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~哦，不知道。能活着逃走就行，闭嘴吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Shit, I'm sorry. I'll stick to blind optimism.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~操，对不起。怪我没有盲目乐观。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Listen, Lou, would you mind paying Mori a visit. He says he needs help with something.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~听着，Lou，你能拜访下Mori吗？他说有事情需要帮忙。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Rocco's gonna be pissed if you're not down there soon.
~z~I can't handle anything on my own. It's amazing I don't ask you to come take a piss for me.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~我一个人什么都不行。没让你帮我拉尿已经很不错了。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You fucking missed me you, you piece of shit. Fucking prick.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~你他妈没打中啊，你个废物，你个傻逼。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Good idea. Lets have you put us out of business.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~真不错，等着被你搞到倒闭吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Thank the fun police for that little jail dodger. When are you going to settle down, Luis?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~谢谢快乐杀手的避免犯法小知识啊。~n~你什么时候才能安定下来，Luis？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Thanks, Lou. Look. I'm sorry about this shit.
~z~Running away from mobsters in a motherfucking golf cart? I think you got us here, T. Thanks for that.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~开着傻逼高尔夫球车摆脱黑帮？我看是你害的，T。谢谢你啊。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~There was a time when the name Tony Prince meant something downtown.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~想当年Tony Prince还是城里响当当的名号。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Thanks, Lou. Sweet of you to say so.
~z~Pussy makes him do stranger things, but luckily I'm not susceptible to those perils like you are.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~娘们会让人失大智。好在我不会像你一样，遇到红颜祸水。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~I need you to help me get some information out of this union prick who's decided to get an over inflated opinion of himself.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~我要你帮我从这个自以为是的工会傻逼嘴里问点话。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~I ain't never handled that shit, but it can't be that tough.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~这我还真没试过，不过也没多难吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Get down there, Lou. What are you waiting for?
~z~Oh really, Tone? When did you become the golf buggy specialist?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~真的假的，Tone？你什么时候成了高尔夫球车专家啊？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~the wolves are baying for blood, and the guy who's meant to be my rock has become a bitter and cynical prick.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~嗜血的群狼环伺，该当我后盾的人却成了悲观刻薄的混蛋。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Okay, I'm helping with the shooting this time. You can't carry me through this like you did in Dim Sum Plaza.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~好了，这次我会帮着开枪的。你别想像上次在点心广场那样护着我了。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Get down there. We're fucked if Rocco gets killed.
~z~I know he's a bit of a schmuck, but we owe the man money and I don't want him anywhere near the clubs.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~我知道他有点混蛋，但我们欠着他钱，我不想让他靠近夜店。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Right before she taught you how to suck a dick, Rocco? Get out a here.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~在她教你吹鸡巴之前教的吗，Rocco？快滚蛋吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Everything's gonna turn out just perfect, because Tony says so, and he never makes mistakes.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~结果一定很完美，因为Tony这么说了，而且他从不犯错。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yeah, well, being his stooge's stooge ain't too much glamor neither.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~是啊，做他狗腿子的狗腿子，也没光彩到哪去。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~or the city goes on a noise control push, or we need to file a tax return?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~城市开始控制噪音了呢？哪天要报税了呢？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yo, T. I just love your new friends. Fucking fantastic guys.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~呦，T，我爱死你的新朋友了。都他妈是帮能人。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Alright, bro, cool. I mean shit, if you don't wanna save money. Car jacking makes economical sense, that's all. Later.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~好吧，兄弟，没事。他妈的，不想省钱就算了。抢车多经济实惠，就这。再见。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Oh, baa da boom. I'm sure I woulda found that funny if I spoke spic.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~噢，这人真是。我懂西语的话应该就能找到笑点了吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~These fucking guys, stuck in the 1970s or something.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~工会的狗东西，以为自己还活在七十年代是吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Push it, Lou. Come on. We're nowhere near top speed in this thing.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~油门踩到底，Lou。快点。还没跑到这玩意的最高速度。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~There wouldn't have been a job for you if I wasn't the kind of guy people occasionally wanted to kill!
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~要不是我经常被人追杀，哪轮得到你当保镖。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~At the moment, I'm afraid. See you.
~z~Don't worry, L. I ain't gonna chicken out on you like I did in Chinatown.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~别担心，L。这次我不会像上次在唐人街那样当缩头乌龟了。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~If you think I signed up to be this boy scout mafioso's stooge with a big grin on my face...
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~你以为我当这个黑手党小屁孩的狗腿子，是心甘情愿吗...

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You think you're ready for that? You know who to grease when the licenses expire,
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~你真觉得自己很能吗？营业执照过期了找谁打点？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yo Rock, you've invested in the wrong clubs, man. Maybe Split Sides is more your vibe.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~哟，Rock，你这夜店买错了，哥们。喜剧俱乐部更适合你。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~He doesn't! I don't think at least. Do you think he does? All that pent up suburban hard man angst.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~的确不是，至少我觉得不是。你觉得像吗？完全是乡下人装硬汉。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~He can take my money, blackmail me, put a gun to my head,
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~他能抢我的钱、敲诈我、拿枪指着我，

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~What is with that guy and moving the cart?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~那人是有什么毛病，一直挪车？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Can someone tell Rocco there's no reason to move it?
~z~What happened to that Margot girl, anyway? She was nice. Or that English one, Rose, wasn't it?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~那个叫Margot的姑娘怎么了？她挺不错的。还有那个英国人，Rose是吧？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~I don't actually. The kid might just want some company. Can you blame him?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~谁知道啊，说不定只是小屁孩想找人打球了。你能怪他吗？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Tony, shit, you got burrito breath. You ain't been eating Mexican again have you?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~Tony，你他妈一股卷饼味，是不是又吃墨西哥菜了？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~What a fucking tragedy. He'll be sadly missed.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~真是太悲剧了，沉痛哀悼他吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Here we are, bro. Rest up okay.
~z~So sue me, I got a type.
~z~Tone, you mind if we don't discuss my seed and what I do with it?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~Tone，能不能别提什么留种不留种的？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You should get some T-shirts made, T. Get out of the nightclub business and concentrate on your philosophical sayings.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~你可以找人生产文化衫了，T。别搞夜店这行了，多写点至理名言吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Something's gonna have to go our way soon, Tone. I can feel it. See you soon, okay.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~总会有成功的机会的，Tone。我有预感。回见，好吗。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Sarcasm. Great. Just what I need right now. The world is crashing down around us,
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~阴阳怪气，真棒。我现在可太需要了。天都快塌下来了，

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Enjoy your youth, Luis. You don't appreciate it until it's over.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~珍惜青春年华，Luis。只有失去了才会懂得珍惜。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~We doing something for Rocco? The kid who took your money?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~这次要帮Rocco办事？抢你钱的那个小屁孩？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yeah, thank you, but I don't believe it.
~z~Alright. Alright. Maybe I have taken you for granted. I'll change. I'll be better.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~好吧，好吧。是我想当然了。我会改的，我会变好的。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Spreading all that seed of yours has got to get exhausting, never mind messy.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~四处留种一定很累吧？何况还纠缠不清。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yeah. Keep that smile on your face until after the whole Ancelotti family comes down on us.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~是啊。还搁那傻笑呢，我们马上就要被Ancelotti家族追杀了。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Hey you know, I'm really warming to that guy. Like a bad case of crabs.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~我说，我可太喜欢他了，像喜欢死螃蟹一样喜欢。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~He might just like driving it. He still is JUST a brat after all.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~他说不定就喜欢开车，毕竟还只是个小屁孩。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~The fake tan and muscles can be confusing.
~z~Oh yeah, I'll look back on these years of getting shot at and helping you clean up puke as the best times of my life.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~是啊，我会怀念这段穿梭枪林弹雨、帮你清理呕吐物的美好时光的。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You think I like running around for that little shit?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~你以为我喜欢替那个小屁孩跑腿？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Tony, man, you got to calm down. You're really pushing it.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~Tony兄弟，你冷静点。这样有点过了。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Wow. What a champ. I love that guy.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~哇哦。这就是天才吗。我爱死那家伙了。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~I know everything that happens in the clubs. I may be a washed up old has been, but I pay attention.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~店里就没有我不知道的事。我可能是有点过气了，但眼光还是有的。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Let me handle things for a while. At least until we get out of this shit.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~让我来收拾这堆烂摊子，直到我们摆脱困境。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You been reading my Lovemeet profile? "Lonely old has been seeks crazy coke head with bulging orange biceps."
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~你看过我的觅爱网简介吗？「寂寞老男人，寻找拥有橙色饱满二头肌的可卡因疯子。」

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~but if I'm caught in bed with him it's me who goes to jail.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~但万一我和他被捉奸在床，要进局子的是我。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~This is a new Tony Prince you got here, L. Not that gunshy pussy you shleped through Chinatown.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~我现在是全新的Tony Prince，L。不是那个在唐人街被你护着的胆小鬼了。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Crabs are easier to get rid of. Believe me on that one.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~螃蟹比他好对付多了，我可没乱说。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Listen, Tone. Maybe you should take a holiday. Get down to Vice City. The Caribbean maybe.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~听着，Tone。你最好去度个假吧。去趟罪城，或者是加勒比。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Sorry, man, but I really got us in the shit here, Luis.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~对不起，伙计。碰上这种事都是我害的，Luis。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Until it comes time to protect your ass from whoever you got your fatwa of the day from.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~直到被人追杀了，你才想起来找我救命。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yeah yeah you fuck, you missed me bitch. ~n~ I'm gonna get down and talk to him.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~是啊，是啊，操你妈的，你他妈打不中我。~n~－我要下去跟他好好聊聊。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You SEEK attention. I'll give you that.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~是渴求别人的目光吧。我满足你。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Hey don't worry about it. Getting shot at, it's all in a day's work.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~嘿，没必要道歉的。变成枪战，这也挺正常的。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Shit, I'm not nearly medicated enough to comtemplate what might happen next. See ya, Lou.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~妈的，嗑的药不够多，我都不敢想接下来会发生什么。再见，Lou。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You know what we're needed for at the driving range?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~他叫我们去高尔夫球场干嘛？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Rock should get a job at this place.
~z~Yeah. Sure. You could call crazy coke addict moron a type.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~没咋，喜欢可卡因疯子是你自己的事。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~I don't think they could do you for driving while intoxicated in this.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~开这玩意总不会判你酒驾毒驾。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~T, bro, you should get one of these for getting between the club.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~喂，T，买台这个当夜店间的接驳车吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Because some of the girls I seen you with, I could swear their parents must have signed consent forms.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~跟你一块儿的姑娘里面，有几个好像都没到合法年龄吧？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Didn't it seem surprising that I wanted a violent criminal on board in the first place?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~谢谢你的阴阳怪气。光是会找残暴的罪犯搭伙就很奇怪了吧？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yes. One of the joys of getting old is being ordered around by people below the age of consent in Utah.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~没错。中年人的一大乐趣就是被未成年小鬼使唤。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~I guess I got to go car shopping, and before you suggest it, I'm not gonna let you "boost" one for me.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~只能去买新车了。我知道你想说啥，用不着你帮我去「搞」一辆车。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Rocco struck me as an insecure prick, but I didn't think he rolled like that.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~虽然Rocco像个危险分子，但他不是同性恋吧。
~z~我们是生意伙伴，我们共享一切。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Money makes a man do strange things.
~z~then maybe things would be holding together, better.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~也不至于落到现在这个地步。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Real shame, I'll have to ask my maid to translate for me.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~可惜我只能叫女佣帮我翻译。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~It was Daisy, bro. How you know about that shit, anyway?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~人家叫Daisy，兄弟。你都从哪听说的？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~I left you to it, T. I thought you could handle this on your own. Sorry, bro.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~都交给你了，T。我还以为你一个人能行。抱歉，兄弟。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Toto don't get you killed nearly as much, if recent times is anything to go by.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~考虑到最近的遭遇，至少女人不会让你差点没命。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~I'm the only one who knows how to keep us from drowning in it.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~只有我才能让大家不被烧死。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You don't ever let me into the serious shit. And you do deals without even telling me.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~管正经事没我的份。跟别人谈生意也不通知我一声。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Whenever I come to the clubs you ask me to run off on some stupid errand like a chump.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~我每次来夜店，都被你派出去干傻逼活，跟白痴一样。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Shit, if you and Evan is an example of a long-term relationship, I'm going to steer clear.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~操，要是你和Evan算是模范夫妻，我还是敬而远之吧。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Yo, Rocco, you piece of shit, what you get us into?
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~呦，Rocco，你这混蛋，拉我们下水是吧？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~Fucking Rocco! After what happened in Chinatown, please tell me we gonna take a nine iron to his legs.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~傻逼Rocco！在唐人街出了那种事，我们能不能往他腿上来一棍子？

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~You missed. You swing like a fag.
E2T5BAU.translated: ~z~这都打不着。挥杆还跟个基佬似的。

E2T5BAU.original: ~z~What the fuck is with these fucks?
